Mr. Lewis has been our Chief Executive Officer since our spin-off from Ventas, Inc. in 2015. Previously, he served as President of Ventas from 2010 to 2015, as Executive Vice President and Chief Investment Officer of Ventas from 2006 to 2010, and as Senior Vice President and Chief Investment Officer of Ventas from 2002 to 2006. 


View Profile 



